How to Run the Project:
To run this project locally:

Clone the GitHub repository:
git clone https://github.com/Vasantha2127/Ethical-phishing-simulator

Navigate into the folder:
cd ethical-phishing-simulator

Install Flask:
pip install flask

Initialize the database:
python models.py

Start the Flask server:
python app.py

Open your browser and go to:
http://localhost:5000

The application will allow you to create phishing templates, simulate phishing links, log user clicks, and view analytics. Detailed instructions are available in the project's README.md file.

